query:
INSERT INTO auction (
                    name,
                    description,
                    transaction_id,
                    owner_id
                ) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?)
                RETURNING
                    id,
                    name,
                    description,
                    owner_id,
                    transaction_id,
                    settled_price as "settled_price: _",
                    ? as "transaction_timestamp!: _"
